```

### Three Agents

| Agent | Strategy | P(escalation) | T_recover | F_load |
|-------|----------|---------------|-----------|--------|
| Sentiment-Only | Classify emotion → canned reply | 0.063 ± 0.021 | 1.28 | 28.54 |
| Static-Valence | Fixed positive reply always | 0.000 ± 0.000 | 0.00 | 9.24 |
| NEPA-HRI | Stability envelope + TD learning | 0.093 ± 0.042 | 1.68 | 26.09 |

**Note:** Static-Valence scores low escalation by suppressing all reactivity —
it masks instability rather than managing it. NEPA-HRI operates under
full incident stress (5 injections per episode) and actively controls
the trajectory inside Ω.

